[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    537[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m11[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mClose the LOW voice findings[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m (V1, V2, V3, V4, V5). Replace future-dated timestamps; tighten performance-benchmark caveats; resolve industry-figure TODOs (NEWS2/MEWS operational performance, current FDA CDS guidance, Wong et al. JAMA Internal Medicine citation, HIPAA-eligible Bedrock model list); tighten sample narrative's "consideration of empiric antibiotic timing" phrasing; add cross-reference between The Honest Take's "build the workflow first" lesson and the Implementation-Time Tier table's Basic tier.[K
